NAME		i3ctl
SYNTAX		i3ctl <subcommand> [arguments] ...
DESCRIPTION	Control the intermud-III system.

		i3ctl close			- Disconnect from router.
		i3ctl open			- Connect to router.
		i3ctl send <string>		- Send a string to router.
		i3ctl hosts dump		- Flush host list to disk.
		i3ctl chan			- List channels.
		i3ctl chan delete		- Delete channel list.
		i3ctl chan <channel> tunein	- Tune talker into <channel>.
		i3ctl chan <channel> tuneout	- Tune talker out of <channel>.

